name: [v0.0.6-rc8] pre-deployment
body:
## What's Changed
* Audit reverts by @yorhodes in https://github.com/many-things/cw-hyperlane/pull/82
* Pausable ISM by @nambrot in https://github.com/many-things/cw-hyperlane/pull/84
* Allow threshold == set size and add tests by @nambrot in https://github.com/many-things/cw-hyperlane/pull/85
* Do not revert on dispatch due to excess funds by @yorhodes in https://github.com/many-things/cw-hyperlane/pull/86
* fix: coverage by @byeongsu-hong in https://github.com/many-things/cw-hyperlane/pull/87
* Make domain hash use left padded mailbox addresses by @yorhodes in https://github.com/many-things/cw-hyperlane/pull/88
* Implement simple protocol fee hook by @yorhodes in https://github.com/many-things/cw-hyperlane/pull/89
* fix: remove redundant protobuf by @byeongsu-hong in https://github.com/many-things/cw-hyperlane/pull/90
* feat: use optimizer by @byeongsu-hong in https://github.com/many-things/cw-hyperlane/pull/92
* Add mailbox unit tests for post dispatch by @yorhodes in https://github.com/many-things/cw-hyperlane/pull/91
* fix: pr and test by @byeongsu-hong in https://github.com/many-things/cw-hyperlane/pull/93
* feat: testnet deployment by @byeongsu-hong in https://github.com/many-things/cw-hyperlane/pull/94

## New Contributors
* @yorhodes made their first contribution in https://github.com/many-things/cw-hyperlane/pull/82

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/many-things/cw-hyperlane/compare/v0.0.6-rc7...v0.0.6-rc8
